LOCUS       Gateway_attP1            232 bp    DNA              UNK 01-JAN-1980
DEFINITION  Gateway (lambda-derived) attP1 attachment site; 232 bp, the
            specificity-1 donor-vector recombination site from pDONR221. The BP
            reaction (lambda Int + IHF) recombines it only with the cognate
            attB1 to give attL1 + attR1, enforcing directional recombinational
            cloning..
ACCESSION   Gateway_attP1
VERSION     Gateway_attP1
